Following, you can find a complete example on how to adjust the selected rows, using the [`ListSelectionModel`](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/javax/swing/ListSelectionModel.html), including [`MouseEvent#getModifiers`](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/awt/event/MouseEvent.html) checks. After that, it is possible to open a (optional) [`JPopupMenu`](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/javax/swing/JPopupMenu.html).

